We are one of the most sought-after caterers in Key Largo, for our exceptional service, variety of serving styles, and award-winning food! Our menus, crafted with attention to detail, are inspired by the very individuals who chose to have their weddings with us. Each catering menu is a testament to the 2000+ Florida Keys Weddings we have successfully catered. BRINGING CULINARY DREAMS TO LIFE WITH KEY LARGO CONCH HOUSE CATERING Destination Wedding Catering and Venue for Key Largo, Islamorada, Florida Keys! From locally sourced seafood and produce, every dish served aims to amplify the joy and love that fill the air on your wedding day. A collaboration with Key Largo Conch House is more than just hiring a caterer; it’s entrusting your culinary dreams to a Key Largo Catering team that values your vision as much as you do. Because to us every plate we serve is a chapter in your love story, and we are committed to making each chapter as memorable as possible. We cater throughout Key Largo and Islamorada in the beautiful Florida Keys! About key largo conch house Key Largo Conch House A second generation, family owned and operated, seafood restaurant and wedding caterer since 2004. Our caring and committed staff is excited to present their vision to you. They want you have a fantastic experience and enjoy fresh, local seafood. We've been featured on The Travel Channel, Food Network, Emeril's Florida, how to DO florida, Florida Keys Best Restaurants and more. Come find out why we're getting all this attention! Key Largo & Islamorada Catering Planning an event in the Florida Keys? Contact us today! We specialize in wedding catering and special events catering - servicing Key Largo and Islamorada in the Florida Keys. Be sure to follow us on Instagram for great catering ideas! @klconchhouse_events Florida Keys Catering Menus Seasonal and Local We refuse to compromise on quality in our seafood restaurant. That's why we source our fresh ingredients from local farmers and seafood markets. No matter what time of year, you can be sure you're eating the best of the season! Fresh, local seafood and produce is our motto. We have the same standards for coffee. We only serve Segafredo, so come by for a latte, cappuccino or espresso. Voted best coffee in Key Largo every year! Travel Channel, Food Network, Emeril's Florida and more... desserts. Key Largo Conch House is family owned, and operated. An environmentally friendly restaurant that serves sustainable seafood. We were featured on Emeril’s Florida March 2015, Travel Channel’s Man v Food 2012, Discovery Channel 2013, and The Food Network 2007.
